varies from 400to 600V.   A ‘leaktransformer   performs 
the dual role of providing the ignition voltage initially, and 
acting as a choke for   limiting the   current subsequently 
whenthe lamp starts conducting. The   diagramofaleak 
transformer is shown in Fig 5. 
